title: 06/30/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 06/30/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Bucks/Hawks game with Bucks Color Analyst Marques Johnson. With both stars hurt, which team has the advantage at this point in the series? Hall of Famer and Hawks VP Dominique Wilkins calls in to discuss the chances we'll see Trae Young back for Game 5. And Men in Blazers co-host Roger Bennett joins us to discuss England's win in the Euro Cup against Germany.
